<p>How can i store last value of <code>$total['value']</code> into <code>$COD</code>?</p>  <p>Variable and echo it and other place of page code is </p>  <pre><code> &lt;?php foreach( $wpo_wcpdf-&gt;get_woocommerce_totals() as $key =&gt; $total ) : ?&gt;     &lt;tr class="&lt;?php echo $key; ?&gt;"&gt;         &lt;td class="no-borders"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;         &lt;th class="description"&gt;&lt;?php echo $total['label']; ?&gt;&lt;/th&gt;         &lt;td class="price"&gt;&lt;span class="totals-price"&gt;&lt;?php echo $total['value']; ?&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;     &lt;/tr&gt;    &lt;?php endforeach; ?&gt; </code></pre>  <p>This code of "WooCommerce PDF Invoices &amp; Packing Slips" free plugin</p>